title: Genasi of Fire
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

As a fire [[genasi]], you gain the following benefits.

* You have [[darkvision]] within 60 feet. Everything you see in darkness is in a shade of red.
* You are resistant to fire.
* You can cast one of the following spells: [[produce flame]], [[control flames]], [[burning hands]], [[scorcher]], or [[flame blade]].